# Wi-Fi Stats App



A simple app that displays Wi-Fi network statistics on macOS using FastAPI and 
Next.js.



## Requirements



- macOS

- Python 3.10+

- Node.js 18+



## Setup



### 1. Backend (Python)



```
cd backend

pip install -r requirements.txt

```


### 2. Frontend (Next.js)



```
cd frontend

npm install

```


## Run



Start both servers in separate terminals:



### Backend

```
cd backend

uvicorn main:app --reload

```


### Frontend

```
cd frontend

npm run dev

```


Open your browser at http://localhost:3000 to see the Wi-Fi stats.

